  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "Debug the code in the IDE.\n\nThe code is supposed to do the following:\n\n\nInput three space-separated integers on a single line.\nIf the middle integer is greater than the sum of the other two integers and is odd, print 1; otherwise, print 0.",
    "constraints": [
      "1 <= T <= 100",
      "1 <= a, b, c <= 100"
    ],
    "inputFormat": "First line contains an integer T, the number of test cases. Each of the next T lines contains three space-separated integers a, b and c.",
    "outputFormat": "For each test case, print 1 if b is greater than a + c and b is odd, otherwise print 0. Each answer on its own line.",
    "sampleTestCases": [
